data.description: Welcome To This Updated Home in A Peaceful Centennial Hills Community! Move In Ready and Clean! The Home’s Front Yard Hedges Are Water Smart and Maintenance Free. The Living Room Opens To Your Kitchen With Granite Counter Tops and Stainless Steel Appliances (all included with Washer and Dryer!) Beautiful Lighting From Windows Throughout the Home. Primary Bedroom Is Away From The Living Area For Maximum Privacy. Backyard With High Back Wall and Trees, Perfect For BBQs + Entertaining, Just In Time For Spring! Garage is Epoxied and Easy To Clean! Plan Your Home Tour Today!
